data.title: Barry Keoghan stars in girlfriend Sabrina Carpenter's new music video
data.meta_description: Barry Keoghan has starred in girlfriend Sabrina Carpenter's new music video.
data.text:
Barry Keoghan has starred in girlfriend Sabrina Carpenter's new music video.

The US singer has released her new single, Please Please Please, from her upcoming sixth album.

Short n' Sweet is set to be released on August 23rd.

The Espresso singer's real-life boyfriend, Dubliner Barry Keoghan, stars in the brand new music video for her latest release.

The video begins with Carpenter sitting in a jail cell, having been arrested at the end of her Espresso music video.

As she's being released, the singer catches the eye of real-life boyfriend Keoghan as he's getting dragged into prison.

The 25-year-old is later seen waiting for him outside as he is released, before more crimes are committed and he ends up back inside.

Please Please Please premiered on Friday, ahead of her new album release in August.
